snippet.title: 100 Kids Vs World's Strongest Man!
snippet.description:
No one could have predicted that outcome at the end lol

Feastables launched a new variety bag in Costco just in time for Halloween so you can give out mini sizes of our favorite flavors to trick-or-treaters! Find a store near you üëâ https://www.costco.com/w/-/locations FeastablesPartner
